Rating: 0
Rather bland. To add interest: Delete beans Add extra garlic and two hot dried chili peppers to vegetables after they are in the skillet for a few minutes. Sprinkle fresh thyme, salt and pepper on fish and place on top of vegetables in the skillet. Cover and cook on low heat for 10 - 15 minutes. Serve with lemon wedges and fresh chopped parsley.

