Rating: 3
I used petrale sole. The fish only needed 2 minutes per side and was very delicate - the fillets started falling apart in the pan. I suspect this type of fish needs to be breaded before cooking, to help hold it together.

Rating: 4
Excellent dish for a supper party easy to prepare in advance and quick to cook. I used lemon sole and the flavour was delicious.